#- §o8 December, 2012§0
§0
§0
§0
§0Ah, Mt. Augusta. A§0
§0place of great history.§0
§0It is great to return§0
§0to this city - and how§0
§0much it has developed§0
§0over the months! I'm§0
§0surprised every time I§0
§0enter through the§0
§0portal.§0

#- Today is a momentus§0
§0day, in that the§0
§0Civcraft Fist Fighting§0
§0League is holding their§0
§0first tournament.§0
§0Sixteen contestants§0
§0will enter the§0
§0brackets, but only one§0
§0will emerge victorious. §0

#- No eqiupment will be§0
§0allowed into the boxing§0
§0ring, so contestants§0
§0must rely solely on§0
§0their own strength and§0
§0skill.§0
§0
§0
§0

#- ---First Round of§0
§0Fighting---§0
§0
§0Fight #1-§0
§0Chaseinvaders vs.§0
§0R3KoN§0
§0
§0A quick start, with an§0
§0unbelieveably swift§0
§0finish by R3KoN,§0
§0knocking§0
§0Chaseinvaders right§0
§0out of the arena.§0

#- Fight #2- Tutterise vs.§0
§0Amoroy§0
§0
§0A slow start, the two§0
§0combantants swuing at§0
§0each other for a good§0
§0long time before§0
§0finally Amoroy is§0
§0beaten into submission.§0
§0The crowd goes wild§0
§0as Tutterise holds his§0
§0fists aloft in victory.§0

#- Fight #3- Lister33 vs.§0
§0Its Raining§0
§0
§0Lister hangs back for§0
§0a quick moment, forcing§0
§0Raining to rush§0
§0forward and take the§0
§0offensive; Lister§0
§0quickly ducks around§0
§0Raining's punches,§0
§0catches his opponent§0
§0in a jump, knocking§0
§0Raining right out of§0

#- the ring.§0

#- Fight #4- SilentSeekr§0
§0vs. Goatsedotcx§0
§0
§0The two jump right into§0
§0each other, going for§0
§0a quick offensive. The§0
§0fight goes back and§0
§0forth until finally,§0
§0Seekr is backed into a§0
§0corner and beaten§0
§0down by Goatse's quick§0
§0strikes.§0
§0

#- ---Second Round of§0
§0Fighting---§0
§0
§0Allowing R3KoN the§0
§0first move, Fox stays§0
§0in his corner, taking a§0
§0few punches before§0
§0ducking out into the§0
§0center of the arena.§0
§0However, R3KoN takes§0
§0several hard punches§0
§0while missing his own,§0
§0evening the fight out.
#- The two slug each§0
§0other for quite a while§0
§0before finally Fox§0
§0downs R3KoN with a§0
§0finishing, crushing hit.§0
§0
§0Fight #2- Scainburger§0
§0vs. Tuttertise§0
§0
§0Scain rushes in§0
§0quickly, meeting Tutter§0
§0near the latter's side§0
§0of the ring, but the§0

#- fight is quickly evened.§0

#- Scain overextends§0
§0himself too quickly,§0
§0getting pushed into a§0
§0corner. In a§0
§0desperate fight to§0
§0stay alive, he flees to§0
§0the center, but is§0
§0knocked unconcsious§0
§0by Tutter's amazing§0
§0blows.§0
§0
§0Fight #3- GabeKnight§0
§0vs. Lister33§0

#- 
§0Gabe goes on a quick§0
§0offensive,§0

#- trapping Lister in his§0
§0corner for a moment§0
§0before the battle§0
§0moves to the center. It§0
§0stays there while the§0
§0two hardily trade hits§0
§0until finally GabeKnight§0
§0goes down in a blaze§0
§0of glory. A long,§0
§0hard-won fight for§0
§0Lister.§0

#- Fight #4- DanalGore§0
§0vs. Goatsedotcx§0
§0
§0The two circle around§0
§0each other before§0
§0quickly introducing§0
§0each other to their§0
§0fists. The fight rages§0
§0quickly until Goatse§0
§0catches Danal in a§0
§0quick mid-air hit,§0
§0sending him hurtling§0
§0out of the ring.§0

#- ---Semifinals---§0
§0
§0Fight #1, Round 1-§0
§0Tutterise vs.§0
§0FoxMcLeod3§0
§0
§0Fox stays in his§0
§0corner again, letting§0
§0Tutter come to him. He§0
§0quickly shows he's§0
§0made of more and§0
§0pushes his opponent§0
§0to the center.§0

#- The two circle each§0
§0other quickly and are§0
§0at it again and it ends§0
§0in a double knockout!§0
§0Unbelieveable! It will go§0
§0as a tie!§0
§0
§0Fight #1, Round 2-§0
§0Tutterise vs.§0
§0FoxMcLeod3§0
§0
§0Tutter rushes in,§0
§0catching Fox in his§0

#- corner yet again and§0
§0trapping him this time.§0

#- The worried Fox tries§0
§0to get out, but is§0
§0caught by heavy§0
§0consecutive blows by§0
§0the relentless Tutter,§0
§0ending in a Fox's§0
§0knockout!§0
§0
§0Fight #1, Round 3-§0
§0Tutterise vs.§0
§0FoxMcLeod3§0
§0
§0Fox charges in this§0

#- time and the two meet§0
§0in the center,§0

#- beating each other§0
§0with no mercy. They§0
§0jump and circle, each§0
§0trying to land the best§0
§0hit, but after a long,§0
§0hard beating, Fox goes§0
§0down and Tutter claims§0
