#- Fight #2, Round 1-§0
§0Lister33 vs.§0
§0Goatsedotcx§0
§0
§0Goatse rushes in but§0
§0Lister flees his§0
§0corner to get around§0
§0his opponent. The two§0
§0seem to have an equal§0
§0footing, each staying§0
§0in the center, but§0
§0Goatse quickly cinches§0
§0the victory with a§0

#- staggering KO!§0

#- Fight #2, Round 2-§0
§0Lister33 vs.§0
§0Goatsedotcx§0
§0
§0The two quickly meet in§0
§0the center, both§0
§0jumping for extra§0
§0impact, however they§0
§0are met evenly,§0

#- and as Goatse§0
§0changes his fighting§0
§0style and decides to§0
§0stay planted on the§0
§0ground, Lister§0
§0continues his jumps,§0
§0eventually being§0
§0caught directly at the§0
§0wrong time and§0
§0launched right out of§0
